==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immigrant
<hw>Im"mi*grant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>immigrans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>immigrare</ets> to go into: cf. F.
<ets>immigrant</ets>. See <er>Immigrate</er>.]</ety> <def>One who
immigrates; one who comes to a country for the purpose of permanent
residence; -- correlative of <xex>emigrant</xex>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- See <er>Emigrant</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immigrate</ent>⟦br⟧
